<section>
  <title>Preferences Widget</title>
  <para id="preferencesWidget"><informalexample>
      <para><screenshot>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
              <imagedata fileref="images/preferencesWidget.png"/>
            </imageobject>
            <caption>Menu tab preference options</caption>
          </mediaobject>
        </screenshot></para>
      <para>When specifying a preferred menu style, you are presented with the
      following options:<note>
          <para>For a complete list of all the toolbar buttons available for
          each module, see <xref linkend="Section476479"/>.</para>
        </note></para>
      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Show Inventory Menu</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Inventory</guimenu> module
            menu on the user's main application window.</para>
            <variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>Show Inventory Toolbar</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Inventory</guimenu>
                  module toolbar buttons on the user's main application
                  window.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Show Products Menu</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Products</guimenu> module
            menu on the user's main application window.</para>
            <variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>Show Products Toolbar</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Products</guimenu>
                  module toolbar buttons on the user's main application
                  window.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry role="standard">
          <term>Show Schedule Menu</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> module
            menu on the user's main application window.</para>
            <variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>Show Schedule Toolbar</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Schedule</guimenu>
                  module toolbar buttons on the user's main application
                  window.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Show Purchase Menu</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select to display the <guimenu>Purchase</guimenu> module
            menu on the user's main application window.</para>
            <variablelist>
